snippet.textDisplay:
I am a Brit living in Colorado and i am so bloody sick of everyone making such a HUGE issue of Harry and Meaghan making decisions for their family and happiness.
I'm sickened of the way every single nuance of their public appearances is torn to shreds not only by the paparazzi; but tabloids, mainstream media, and the world press.

This isnt them turning their back on the Royal family: its preservation of their relationship; their marriage; their family and their very lives. Its not even an unprecedented move by members of the Royal Household.
This couple already have a law suit against the tabloids for the disgusting; slanderous comments and accusations that are continuously made against them.
Harry has made it perfectly clear from the very start that he will NOT tolerate his wife and son being pursued and continuously harrassed and berated by anyone. And if such things did occur he would hold those responsible to task fir their actions.
To quote "I lost my mother to these parasites; i willnot risk my wife and child suffering the same persecution"

Last; but not least, Harry is now fifth in line for the throne; behind William and his three children. It would suffer our Royal Family to be dealt an earth shattering blow before he would take on the role of King. With the laws of accession to the throne being changed back in the 80s; Princess Charlotte takes her rightful place behind her older brother and in front of her younger brother i the immediate line of sucession. If Kate and William decide to have more chikdre; they will take their place in the line of acession accordingly. Then Harry and Louis and any more children that Harry and Meaghan might have.

History buffs will know that until this change was enacted; Prince Louis would; as a male heir, step in front of his sister in the line of sucession; but that is no longer the case.

Harry and Meghan are nio deserting the Royal Family; nor are they shirking their duty towards the Royal Household.

If one does the research of Royal Families of Europe ; one would find various princes, princesses. Dukes and Duchesses, Lords and Ladies scattered all over the world. Many of their expat friends and acquaintences would never know they were of Royal blood.
This also runs true for many of the well established Royal families throughout the entire European continent into the lands of Persia, Mesopotamia; Babylon, even into Russia (if stories of Tsar Nicholas' youngest daughter are to be believed)

Long gone are the days when Royal families all lived under each others noses in an era where romanticised intrigue, murder and scheming were the order if the day and somewhat prevalent). T hey were all cloistered up together and more often than not; history books tell us of the relentless posturing and plotting how to eliminate anyone who stood in their way to power and perhaps to a particular countrys (ever coveted) Crown.

So enough bashing; enough speculation; enough plain bloody nosey questions of where and why Harry and Meaghan choose to live their lives.

Good grief; we have enough really critical crap wrapping its insiduous tentacles around this planet we're killing; more wars; more threats of world obliteration by the proliferation of nuclear weapons both already stock piled and those being manufacturd as we discuss the ins and outs of Harry and his "biracial wife!"; 😱 yet another pointless; rude and disgusting encapsulating description of a beautiful; inelligent and gracious woman who married the man she loved. That nasty; ignorant; prejudicial crap gets right up my nose.

Why should the rest of the world have anything to gossip about them moving to the magnificent country that is Canada. If i had the money and health to make such a move; to escape the insanity that is clutching at america - i most definately would.

So; all of this to say; live and let live. No matter which country we currentky reside in or which country is the home of our eternal heart. It is not a decision that anyone has the right to pick apart and make all kinds of ridiculous accusations and assumptions about.
A damn shame we dont apply that same magnifying glass to the places we currently live in. Iif more people did; we might actually begin to move this divided, stagnating, hate baiting country toward our previous standing; a more civilised position among the other great nations of this world.

T hey were all cloistered up together and more often than not; history books tell us of the relentless posturing and plotting how to eliminate anyone who stood in their way to power and perhaps to a particular countrys (ever coveted) Crown.

So enough bashing; enough speculation; enough plain bloody nosey questions of where and why Harry and Meaghan choose to live their lives.

Good grief; we have enough really critical crap wrapping its insiduous tentacles around this planet we're killing; more wars; more threats of world obliteration by the proliferation of nuclear weapons both already stock piled and those being manufacturd as we discuss the ins and outs of Harry and his "biracial wife!"; 😱 yet another pointless; rude and disgusting encapsulating description of a beautiful; inelligent and gracious woman who married the man she loved. That nasty; ignorant; prejudicial crap gets right up my nose.

Why should the rest of the world have anything to gossip about them moving to the magnificent country that is Canada. If i had the money and health to make such a move; to escape the insanity that is clutching at america - i most definately would.

So; all of this to say; live and let live. No matter which country we currentky reside in or which country is the home of  our eternal heart. It is not a decision that anyone has the right to pick apart and make all kinds of ridiculous accusations and assumptions about.
A damn shame we dont apply that same magnifying glass to the places we currently live in. Iif more people did; we might actually begin to move this divided, stagnating, hate baiting country toward our previous standing; a more civilised position among the other great nations of this world.
